Manu Shayumbhu. Sharachi. Goutami.

00:59:48.528 --> 00:59:51.282
Damash. Bairath. Chakhush. Sabarno.

00:59:51.372 --> 00:59:53.135
Dakhya Saborno. Brahma Saborno.

00:59:53.225 --> 00:59:55.190
Dharma Saborno. Rudra Saborno.

00:59:55.280 --> 00:59:58.193
Rouchya. Bhoutya. Shayambhu.

01:00:00.013 --> 01:00:01.783
He comes and tells me,

01:00:02.228 --> 01:00:05.147
I have written the Samhita.
Please look at it.

01:00:05.237 --> 01:00:07.603
If you don't have a look at it,
I won't be at peace.

01:00:10.295 --> 01:00:13.228
So I said, let me see
what you've written.

01:00:14.528 --> 01:00:16.760
One lakh slokas.

01:00:17.035 --> 01:00:19.315
Oh, my God! What have you done?

01:00:19.505 --> 01:00:22.012
Who will read so much?
Who has the time for it?

01:00:22.345 --> 01:00:24.277
Cut it!

01:00:24.685 --> 01:00:28.610
300. I selected 300 slokas for him.

01:00:28.970 --> 01:00:31.593
I said, keep these,
they will come in handy.

01:00:32.085 --> 01:00:33.460
The rest, he threw away.

01:00:33.550 --> 01:00:36.125
Excuse me...
- I'll tell you about one more Manu.

01:00:37.630 --> 01:00:41.763
It was the Age of White Pigs.

01:00:42.732 --> 01:00:44.712
Before the time
of the Great Destruction.

01:00:45.015 --> 01:00:47.583
One day, the Creator...

01:00:48.213 --> 01:00:50.392
The Creator came and told me,

01:00:51.830 --> 01:00:56.113
I've created humans but where will
they stand? What will they eat?

01:00:56.283 --> 01:00:58.775
Everywhere, there was only water.

01:00:59.262 --> 01:01:03.883
Seeing the state of the earth,
the Creator got scared.

01:01:05.130 --> 01:01:07.642
Seeing his fear,
I felt pity for him.

01:01:07.862 --> 01:01:11.678
I said, don't feel scared.
I am here.

01:01:11.915 --> 01:01:14.770
The science of the sun
is in the clasp of my hand.

01:01:15.045 --> 01:01:17.203
I increased the power of the sun.

01:01:17.480 --> 01:01:20.843
All the water dried up.

01:01:21.005 --> 01:01:23.870
The earth filled up
with forest and trees.

01:01:24.108 --> 01:01:28.515
Lord, did you know Jesus Christ?

01:01:30.203 --> 01:01:34.223
People say crucifixion.

01:01:34.820 --> 01:01:37.580
I say crucifact.

01:01:37.838 --> 01:01:40.345
Because I have seen it
all with my own eyes.

01:01:40.815 --> 01:01:44.835
My God! And Gautama Buddha?

01:01:46.025 --> 01:01:47.348
Gautam?

01:01:49.208 --> 01:01:53.665
That Gautam? Gautam was just
a young lad of yesterday.

01:01:54.668 --> 01:01:58.050
I knew the Buddha
when he was a young lad.

01:01:59.657 --> 01:02:02.915
Tempora.

01:02:03.202 --> 01:02:05.892
Boris.

01:02:06.588 --> 01:02:09.210
Nephic.

01:02:09.300 --> 01:02:11.727
Nitious.

01:02:12.022 --> 01:02:14.452
Nibhus.

01:02:14.622 --> 01:02:17.118
Nibhorus.

01:02:29.625 --> 01:02:30.842
Don't go.

01:02:34.280 --> 01:02:36.330
Fire!

01:02:36.420 --> 01:02:37.940
Fire!

01:02:38.030 --> 01:02:40.065
Fire!

01:02:40.155 --> 01:02:41.808
What's this?

01:02:41.898 --> 01:02:43.608
Fire!

01:02:43.698 --> 01:02:45.468
Fire!

01:02:47.313 --> 01:02:48.695
Fire!

01:02:49.498 --> 01:02:52.273
Fire!

01:02:52.363 --> 01:02:55.303
Fire!

01:03:01.302 --> 01:03:02.940
Fire!

01:03:06.830 --> 01:03:08.512
Fire!

01:03:13.375 --> 01:03:18.573
Hey! Fire!

01:03:27.400 --> 01:03:29.538
Hello. Fire brigade?

01:03:29.628 --> 01:03:31.778
Fire brigade?

01:03:44.778 --> 01:03:47.528
Leave me. What are you doing?

01:03:47.618 --> 01:03:49.897
Leave me. There's a fire.

01:03:49.987 --> 01:03:51.993
Leave me.
- Why?

01:03:52.277 --> 01:03:55.163
Don't you know the science
behind the fire? Lord?

01:04:03.730 --> 01:04:07.908
Now leave, Babaji.
No more in this locality.

01:04:17.978 --> 01:04:21.032
What are you doing?
- Rescue.

01:04:23.975 --> 01:04:25.920
Where is the fire?
- Hold still.

01:04:28.653 --> 01:04:31.948
Can I ask you something?
This is not a quotation.

01:04:32.700 --> 01:04:34.243
My original words.

01:04:34.333 --> 01:04:35.973
Shall I?
- What?

01:04:36.063 --> 01:04:38.868
Will you marry me?

01:04:39.345 --> 01:04:40.520
Oh my God!

01:04:41.718 --> 01:04:43.517
Really?

01:05:27.627 --> 01:05:30.425
Baba!

01:05:35.485 --> 01:05:36.530
Let's go.

01:05:40.398 --> 01:05:43.313
Well, you're not so
silly after all!

01:05:43.685 --> 01:05:46.133
Towards the future. Let's go.

01:05:48.525 --> 01:05:49.648
Let's go.